Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭和平常一样放在桌子上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.53,0:01:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  凛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜  普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:01:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:20.04,comment1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（莉姆的便当）
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↓Title↓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\pos(424,450)\fs+4\b0\3c&H41acff}微笑
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↑Title↑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆独自在家很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然觉得很可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自从来我们这里之后还没笑过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般那个年龄的孩子应该更有精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得没有活力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不应该把她独自留在家里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆在魔界时就一直是那样的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那孩子不怎么表露感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她适应了这边的世界就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆的话一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能找个什么机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  比方说带她出去玩之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想想有什么能让她高兴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是凛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:39.97,comment1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(莉姆的点心)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太  你听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古往今来  研究长生不老的人不计其数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有人认为魔法是万能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其并不能让死者复活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在三界都在进行相关的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我珍贵的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初也是最后的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你为了那个小恋人的事在烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很理解你想隐藏自己对幼女的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷绝不会因此而歧视你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无论如何都认为我是那种人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跟绿叶说了今天早上的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得他应该是最了解让女孩子高兴的方法的人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明显找错了商量的对象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  要想让女性高兴的话当然还是送礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是让我给她买个娃娃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是没明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越小的孩子可塑性就越高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是买泳装吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海边前当然要选泳装了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校泳装一定很适合她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来阻止这个学校泳装狂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土见  又有新恋人来找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种玩笑树开开就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普  普莉姆拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是凛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出什么事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土见Lovers的各位都认识这个孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个称呼很暧昧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土见的恋人们  没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小琳  小琳  是恋人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  光听到就心跳加快…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这种话的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就给我们介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是土见Lovers的新成员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是偶像同好会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉是从魔界来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是奈莉奈的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受魔王之托  现在寄住在我们家里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和没有血缘关系的妹妹在同一个屋檐下生活啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你一说  就让人觉得变得很下流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里出了什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见凛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个没关系的  回家了我给你缝上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后别再因为这种事来学校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:10:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是打过上课铃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土见  又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  她突然来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对不起那个小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但马上就要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上让她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去时要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像埃及的金字塔  英国的巨石遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马丘比丘和摩亨约达罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.70,comment1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马丘比丘(Machu Picchu)南美印加古文明所建之城市  一九一一年由考古学家海伦宾汉发现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:08.81,comment1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩亨约达罗(Mohenjo-Daro)巴基斯坦南部印度河下游区域印  度文明的都市遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出于什么目的  如何建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫长的历史中…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去厕所…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然下起雨  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节的天空还真是不可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才…对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家后要立刻洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这么就感冒了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…不带胸罩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实这件事我倒是没发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有比泳装更优先要买的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  忘记带伞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为男人的我是不可能察觉到这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是好好准备下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内衣的话不能用枫用过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布偶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是缝上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看起来好像有不少地方都坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像很旧的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么特别的意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  莉姆很少说自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不爱说话的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello  小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个买东西的好日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊羽前辈怎么也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为听说要选购可爱的内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:15:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从枫那里听说了  决定来帮你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好给莉姆选合适的内衣可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你们二位来说  比起给普莉姆拉选内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看热闹才是目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到非常不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆喜欢什么样式的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜欢的颜色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就交给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就鼓足干劲好好选吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…今天不是为希亚  而是为普莉姆拉买内衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样小凛  你喜不喜欢这种啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么直接…实在是棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  今天是为普莉姆拉买…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害臊  别害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实很喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的这件怎么样…凛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样  凛  这件也很可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小凛  这种也很喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在外边等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去游戏厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天绝对不会输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去游戏厅打发时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么新游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和普莉姆拉的初次见面就是在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她当时一直在看着抓娃娃机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候我想帮她抓什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很想要的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…确实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  是猫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍文静了点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好像不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆穿成熟点的也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 什么  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  本人也这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是选普通点的会比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  这种怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊羽你真大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来伊羽的兴趣是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个很性感啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位～能过来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊羽前辈  有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就有请今天的主角登场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…凛在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们花了不少时间  他大概先回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他不会这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:19:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  找到不少有趣的内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦恼了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是买了透明内衣或绳内衣之类劲暴的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点就买了  让她们忍住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好  买到了合适的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买了什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给普莉姆拉买了点…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给莉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  普莉姆拉  给你  是手信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手信…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是小礼物啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:20:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先打开看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚见面时  你很想要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和那个不是一模一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛你真有一套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛大人实在是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为凛很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  普莉姆拉能高兴就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初也是最后的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手段越来越高明了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙前辈…
